                                <Run FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#FF8C00">YOUR IDEAS</Run>
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph Margin="20,20,0,0">
                                The
                                <Run FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#FF8C00">ATM ALERT Appication</Run>
                                produces bullish and bearish conditions.  Activating Your Ideas in Charts will display the results.
                            </Paragraph>-->

